270
00:26:55,020 --> 00:26:58,240
Instructor Du, are we still calling the roll?

271
00:26:58,240 --> 00:27:02,800
Yes. People who are absent will be treated as dropouts.

272
00:27:07,440 --> 00:27:10,550
- Xiao Beichen!
- Here!

273
00:27:10,550 --> 00:27:12,820
