399
00:35:26,190 --> 00:35:30,420
Since Cheng’s troops got defeated, they’ve stopped moving forward.

400
00:35:30,420 --> 00:35:33,200
I couldn’t believe they were undergoing restructuring

401
00:35:33,200 --> 00:35:35,080
and restarted their fierce strike.

402
00:35:35,080 --> 00:35:37,580
They avoided the difficult Huyang gate,

403
00:35:37,580 --> 00:35:41,840
seized hold of three different towns and went directly to Yongning.

404
00:35:41,840 --> 00:35:44,780
Yongning doesn’t have the same natural barrier as the Huyang gate.

405
00:35:44,780 --> 00:35:48,890
Facing the toughest Cheng troops, you can imagine how difficult it is for the defensive Ying troop.

406
00:35:48,890 --> 00:35:52,320
If we even lost Yongning,

407
00:35:52,320 --> 00:35:57,000
the next place at risk will be Fengcheng, the economic center in the west of the Zhibei area.

408
00:36:01,390 --> 00:36:04,170
If Xiao Douzi were still alive,

409
00:36:05,560 --> 00:36:07,850
he would probably be running his own tailor shop...

410
00:36:08,660 --> 00:36:11,690
in Beixin City already.

411
00:36:11,690 --> 00:36:14,430
He would be doing what he loved.

412
00:36:21,280 --> 00:36:23,410
I want to tell you guys,

413
00:36:25,480 --> 00:36:27,950
this time, when we go to the battlefield,

414
00:36:28,790 --> 00:36:33,330
we're going into the tiger's lair with our lives at risk.

415
00:36:43,830 --> 00:36:45,480
Brothers.

416
00:36:46,460 --> 00:36:48,690
Class 3 of Semester 5.

417
00:36:49,450 --> 00:36:51,720
We must come back alive.

418
00:37:38,750 --> 00:37:43,750
Hangjing, although I want to go home and see you immediately,

419
00:37:43,750 --> 00:37:46,600
I don't want to wait for even a second.

420
00:37:47,640 --> 00:37:52,770
But I believe you'll understand. You know I'm making the right decision.

421
00:37:53,670 --> 00:37:55,690
Wait for me.

