426
00:38:32,570 --> 00:38:37,510
"In the Fengcheng War, Xiao Beichen once again..."

427
00:38:37,510 --> 00:38:39,770
Commander, what does this say?

428
00:38:39,770 --> 00:38:42,730
- Once again, wins the battle.
- He won again?

429
00:38:42,730 --> 00:38:45,930
What about this? What is he awarded with?

430
00:38:45,930 --> 00:38:48,770
"Young and talented Xiao Beichen

431
00:38:48,770 --> 00:38:52,250
- is awarded the title of Major General."
- Major General?

432
00:38:52,250 --> 00:38:56,710
He is appointed as the Chief of the First Army in the three northern regions.

433
00:38:56,710 --> 00:38:58,680
Chief of Army!

434
00:39:00,960 --> 00:39:05,340
