441
00:39:26,770 --> 00:39:28,210
Yes, Madam!

442
00:39:28,210 --> 00:39:29,630
Go back to your work.

443
00:39:29,630 --> 00:39:32,740
Is it necessary for such a grand celebration?

444
00:39:32,740 --> 00:39:34,950
Of course!

445
00:39:39,610 --> 00:39:42,560
Hangjing, your third brother is coming home tomorrow.

446
00:39:42,560 --> 00:39:46,000
I've been tidying up the house. What do you think?

447
00:39:46,000 --> 00:39:48,350
Nothing could go wrong with Seventh Aunt taking care of it.

448
00:39:48,350 --> 00:39:51,780
You're so sweet. I love hearing the words you say.

449
00:39:51,780 --> 00:39:53,880
Come home earlier tomorrow.

450
00:39:53,880 --> 00:39:56,770
