- Brother! Brother!

490
00:43:20,720 --> 00:43:23,580
- Third Brother!
- Where's our gifts?

491
00:43:23,580 --> 00:43:27,030
Fourth Sister said you must have brought gifts for us. Where's the gift?

492
00:43:27,030 --> 00:43:28,390
You brats.

493
00:43:28,390 --> 00:43:31,100
I do have gifts for you.

